-> Run the docker-compose file to setup mongo db
-> socket.io is a transport protocol that enables real-time, bidirectioanl, event based communication.
-> flask-socketio is the lib that provides the integration between flask and socket.io
-> flask-socketio uses some asynchronous services, either eventlet or gevent, these are networking libs written in python. We will use 


-> Flow of events:
        Join Room 
Server <---------------------- Client
        Join_Room_announcement
Server ----------------------> Client
        Send_Message
Server <---------------------- Client
        Revieve_Message
Server ----------------------> Client
        Leave_room
Server <---------------------- Client
        Leave_room_announcement
Server ----------------------> Client

-> Use the following command to install all the packages from requirements.txt
 pip3 install -r requirements.txt